				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Would like to have a whole lot of fun?  =)  If on a PK server, do the following(if not duel someone first):  Tashani, Mezz, Insipid weakness(oops there goes 50 str...), Gravity flux.  They got no chance.  Repeat starting with mez now that they are stunned.  Careful not to use this around a guard or merchant eheh...no I don't speak from experience...*glances about nervously*  <BR>
<BR>
OH and pick someone who doesn't have any str to begin with.  A caster would most certainly die from one cast of this.  You pull 50 str off and they have only 70 or so to begin with(even that's pushing it), now they're encumbered by 40...that's gonna hurt BAD.  I don't have this spell, so I'm only making this up on the assumptions that were made in the other posts.
