			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Gravity Flux is a very fun spell.  Try this sometime enchanters... find another enchanter with gravity flux, then both cast it with about a one second delay between the time you start casting.  this will send the mob (or group of mobs) up into the air so far you can't see them (even with clip plane turned up to the highest).  they dont take more damage, just the damage from 2 gravity fluxes (a little over 600 total) but it is neat-o to see mobs boosted to the stratosphere.
				</font>
